{"tid":2400832,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"新盤春節前仍旺場 凱滙單日沽57伙","createTime":"2021-02-09T09:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T10:06:20.000Z","uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e934dd3f9b6466d6d82a549dfc1f8333d2b1e065","tid":2400832,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:08:09.000Z","msg":"新盤春節前積極推，觀塘凱滙昨重推，即日成功沽出57伙，有兩組大手客分別以2,400萬及2,800萬各連購兩伙，單日套現逾7億元，本月新盤市場已錄約600宗成交。<br />\n<br />\n一手銷情仍然保持暢旺，多個全新盤及餘貨項目先後推出，信置旗下觀塘凱滙日前亦重推餘貨單位，昨日以價單形式推售132伙，並有72伙招標，折實價770.61萬元入場。<br />\n<br />\n昨天共有約60組準買家到場揀樓。信置集團聯席董事田兆源表示，項目已近現樓，5月將會交樓，而商場亦將於4月開幕，項目受用家及投資者歡迎。昨最終單日成功售出57伙，套現逾7.1億元。據悉，有兩組買家有見凱滙快將入伙，分別以2,400萬及2,800萬連購兩伙作自用及投資用途。"},{"pid":"3bff9419a1f7409526d07ee9d4ae7d7eb20dc435","tid":2400832,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"賣唔哂"},{"pid":"ac888663b051b2651c4a3dfa26b717b1d337b065","tid":2400832,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bff9419a1f7409526d07ee9d4ae7d7eb20dc435","tid":2400832,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:11:32.000Z","msg":"賣唔哂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:18:29.000Z","msg":"支聯辦會包底"},{"pid":"d609207cc2944ce81f37a9b0f54a44061880f128","tid":2400832,"uid":267488,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83de6b2225d2d3c44adb7d42f3a867fb617a281a","tid":2400832,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T12:33:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d27fd1ed6f0a772936ef9361a688e69660e8d2a